---
import Layout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Card from "../../components/CardSection.astro";
import Button from "../../components/Button.astro";

const environmentDescription = `• Reducing energy consumption in factories through automation
• Switching to clean energy sources such as solar power
• Planting trees around the factory to create green spaces
• Conducting training to raise employee environmental awareness
• Organizing activities with local communities, such as public clean-up events and preserving natural water sources`;
---

<Layout title="Environmental Development" lang="en">
  <div class="items-center justify-center">
    <section id="home" class="flex flex-col">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-start">
        <div class="w-full">
          <img
            src="/web_asset/en_dev.png"
            alt="homeHeroAlt"
            class="w-full h-auto"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <section
    id="home_env"
    class="w-full h-auto lg:h-[500px] bg-white pt-20 pb-30 hover:bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center"
  >
    <div
      class="text-center w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto"
      style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25rem;"
    >
      SDK & DYMS recognizes the importance of environmental responsibility in
      every aspect of our business operations. We are committed to being a
      socially and environmentally responsible organization, aligning our
      actions with the Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) and ESG principles
      (Environment, Social, Governance). We focus on developing eco-friendly
      innovations, minimizing the environmental impact of our production
      processes, and collaborating with communities to conserve natural
      resources.
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    id="home_env"
    class="w-full h-auto lg:h-[800px] bg-white pt-20 pb-30 hover:bg-gray-100"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.5fr_2fr] relative h-full">
      <div class="relative flex items-center justify-end px-6 lg:px-12">
        <Card
          title="One of our key initiatives is the “SDK & DYMS Green Mission,” which includes activities such as:"
          description={environmentDescription}
          showButton={false}
        />
      </div>
      <div class="h-full w-full">
        <img
          src="/web_asset/green_mission.jpg"
          alt="Environmental Development"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          style="border-end-start-radius: 0.5rem; border-start-start-radius: 0.5rem;"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
    id="home_env"
    class="w-full h-auto lg:h-[500px] bg-white pt-20 pb-30 hover:bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center"
  >
    <div
      class="text-center w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto"
      style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25rem;"
    >
      SDK & DYMS believes that true sustainability starts from within the
      organization and extends outward through collaboration with employees,
      partners, and communities. We are committed to reducing our organizational
      carbon footprint and leading the way in responsible production, while
      delivering long-term benefits to society and the environment.
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
